songs.title: The Witch
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
The grave, opens its face
For those who fake, the niggas that hate
To those who shame, will all attain
Bring the pain, so bring the pain
'Cause I have nobody to blame
I never did shit to maintain

[Bridge]
Stay down, Stay down
Approach, the witch now
Stay down, Stay down
Approach, the witch now
Stay down, stay down
Approach, the witch now
Stay down, stay down
Approach, the witch now

[Verse]
It remains, when there ain't love
There ain't love, I'm goin' down
It remains, when there ain't love
There ain't love, I'm goin' down

[Outro]
Harmonizing
